<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>EMA515_01_SU_0003_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema515_01.css" />

  <!-- 분수 표현 -->
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema515_01_su_0003">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-type="1" data-text="자기주도 2">
        <span class="blue line" lang="y">배운 내용을 떠올려요</span>
        <span lang="y">카드를 선택하여 이전에 배운 내용을 확인해 봅시다.</span>
      </h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents">
      <ul class="letCheck">
        <li>
          <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
          <div class="front">
            <p class="f32b" lang="y">대분수를 가분수로, <br />가분수를 대분수로 나타내기</p>
          </div>
          <div class="back">
            <div class="operations">
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span>1</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>8</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
          <div class="front">
            <p class="f32b" lang="y">분모가 같은 분수의 <br />덧셈과 뺄셈하기</p>
          </div>
          <div class="back">
            <div class="operations">
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              +
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>5</span>
                  <span>7</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
          <div class="front">
            <p class="f32b" lang="y">통분하기</p>
          </div>
          <div class="back">
            <p class="f32b">
            <div class="operations">
              <span class="bracket-left"></span>
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>3</span>
                  <span>4</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              ,
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="bracket-right"></span>
              →
              <span class="bracket-left"></span>
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>9</span>
                  <span>12</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              ,
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>4</span>
                  <span>12</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span class="bracket-right"></span>
            </div>
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
          <div class="front">
            <p class="f32b" lang="y">분모가 다른 분수의 크기 <br />비교하기</p>
          </div>
          <div class="back">
            <div class="operations">
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>5</span>
                  <span>8</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <img src="../../common_contents/common/img/icon_arrow_right.svg" alt="">
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>7</span>
                  <span>12</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bubble_charactor" data-charactor="1" style="display: none;">
        <div class="bubble" data-point-position="bottom left">
          <p lang="y">카드를 한 번 더 선택하면</p>
          <p lang="y">내용을 볼 수 있어요.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="btn_area">
        <!-- 불필요한 태그 제외 후 사용 -->
        <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>

</html>